reviewText: I was unable to play this product at all. I know that I take the chance, but this one seem to meet the criteria for Australia.
Overall fairly good quality.  Elvis in the early years, plenty of songs, but shallow plots.  For Elvis lovers, fun nevertheless!
I am a huge fan of Elvis and collect anything I can on him. I have all but 7 of his movies. I am working on getting the rest for my collection.

Elvis Four-Movie Collection, Vol. 2 (Blue Hawaii / Easy Come, Easy Go / King Creole / Paradise, Hawaiian Style) This is a Volume 2 and I am hoping for a Volume 3. While I have not seem 3 of the four movies in this volume, I do love Elvis movies!! This is a practical way to collect them all because they come in 4 movies in one volume. The bang for the buck is great and they are great movies!
Nice to watch something without killing and with good music.

I'm just letting you know that there is a later version of ELVIS 4-MOVIE COLLECTION VOLUME 2 selling for less on Amazon. It's at Elvis 4-Movie Collection 2. Somehow these 2 versions have slightly different listings on Amazon, which might prevent people from finding the cheaper one. I did a proper review of this DVD set on the other page.
